title: Gorgeous Community, Great Convenience!
posting_body: This wonderful, gorgeous community resides between Austin and Round Rock.
Being located at the edge of Texas Hill Country, residents enjoy views of rolling hills and wooded terrain,  yet receive city-life convenience.
From hiking, fishing and boating to fine dining, shopping and entertainment, you choose how active or relaxed you want your lifestyle to be.
With the Austin city center only 25 miles away, you can indulge in every aspect of Austin living imaginable.
Convenient to Toll 130 and Toll 45, as well as Highway 79 and IH-35!
Call today to check out this community!
